{"tid":922494,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"二手樓價指數九連挫　按周跌1%","createTime":"2018-11-30T11:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T12:52:34.000Z","uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"380abc17a5846fdb6b6c608f1f0cd5f393aad2a0","tid":922494,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181130/photo/bkn-20181130160153402-1130_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181130182445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181130%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181130160153402-1130_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181130182445&h=202f7d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，CCL八大指數齊跌3周，是2008年11月金融海嘯後再現。<br />\n<br />\n其中中原城市領先指數CCL報177.39點，按周跌1.00%，連跌9周共4.94%。中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報179.34點，按周跌1.01%，連跌9周共5.08%。<br />\n<br />\n近3周九龍區樓價跌幅四區最大，有4.03%。同期新界西跌3.54%，港島跌3.32%，新界東跌1.10%。大型屋苑樓價跌勢明顯擴大，CCL Mass近3周跌3.17%，CCL跌2.93%，CCL跌幅被豪宅拖慢。其中豪宅跌幅較少，而中小型卻較大。近3周CCL(大型單位)跌1.65%，CCL(中小型單位)跌3.17%。"},{"pid":"ce00b09abf87f0a45cea189f525ae4763838ece8","tid":922494,"uid":18086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:00:33.000Z","msg":"年尾，唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f394b1babe79b1cfbb29dea44e425529ebe597","tid":922494,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:30:07.000Z","msg":"1%都算跌？誠意邀請好友立即買新樓"},{"pid":"f02238764ce68b8533e5412e8ba64a87831db28c","tid":922494,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:49:58.000Z","msg":"跌嗰1%唔夠，飲少杯凍飲喺返度啦"},{"pid":"3d1df4f354e4ebb647a78a9ed964e30c63517270","tid":922494,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5549925bb5acaec5ddbca479aef97967c7469271","tid":922494,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"隻乞衣3zero成日J CCL<br />